txt.en: 'I ask of you to count my treasures. Not a gold shall be missing or someone will have to pay.'
'Everything seems to be in order then. Your reward is keeping your life!'
The Haradrim commander's stash can be found in Fushaum Bal South.\n\nYou should count the stash to make sure it is all there.
The Haradrim Commander can be found at Fushaum Bal South.\n\nYou should talk to the Haradrim Commander.
The encampment of Fushaum Bal is a lawless home to evil men once under the command of Sauron.
